                    <div class="card-gradient p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-800/20 hover:border-pulse-purple/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-glow-sm">
                        <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-3">The Challenge</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Oscar's tracks had great ideas but sounded amateur compared to the artists he wanted to compete with. His mixes lacked the punch and clarity of professional releases.</p>
                    </div>

